Note: Parser-side token and ownership-operation constants referenced by statement
Note: parsing. The process-signature keywords (called/takes) and the imperative
Note: 'times' / mutable-borrow markers occupy the keyword-code gaps reserved for
Note: them; the ownership-operation tags classify how a Let/Set/Constant statement
Note: affects a variable's ownership state for the parser's ownership tracker.
