Note: ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note: Token-type constants — values EXACTLY mirror the authoritative lexer emit
Note: values (literals.runa 100-140, lexer.runa identifier 150, delimiters.runa
Note: 200-210, keywords.runa 300-640, operators.runa 600-662). Single source of
Note: truth is the lexer; these are the parser-side mirrors of what tokenize_*
Note: actually stamps into a token's type field (offset 0).
