Constant OWNERSHIP_BORROWED as Integer is 2          Note: Variable borrowed (shared reference)
Constant OWNERSHIP_MUTABLE_BORROWED as Integer is 3  Note: Variable mutably borrowed
Constant OWNERSHIP_MOVED as Integer is 4             Note: Ownership moved out of the variable
Constant OWNERSHIP_CREATED as Integer is 10          Note: Variable freshly created (Let binding)
Constant OWNERSHIP_MODIFIED as Integer is 11         Note: Variable mutated in place (Set)
Constant OWNERSHIP_CONSTANT as Integer is 12         Note: Immutable constant binding

