    Note: Parse a comma-separated list of operand expressions for one inline-assembly
    Note: section (outputs, inputs, or clobbers). Each operand is a full expression
    Note: (typically a string-literal constraint or a register/clobber name). The
    Note: list ends at a section-separating colon, an End keyword, or EOF. Returns a
    Note: List of operand AST nodes (possibly empty).
    If parser is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If

    Let operands be proc create from List
    If operands is equal to 0:
