    Note: Parameters may be empty (0), which is valid

    Note: 5. Parse return type
    Let return_type be proc parse_return_type with parser
    Note: Return type may be empty (0), which means void/no return

    Note: 6. Expect and consume colon
    Let colon_consumed be proc parser_expect_token from Parser with parser, TOKEN_COLON
    If colon_consumed is equal to 0:
        proc parser_report_error from Parser with parser, 2, proc create_from_literal from StringCore with "Expected ':' after Process signature", proc token_get_line from Parser with proc parser_current_token from Parser with parser, proc token_get_column from Parser with proc parser_current_token from Parser with parser
        Return 0
    End If

    Note: 7. Parse body
