        Note: Build the union-type body node (AST_UNION_TYPE = 4002) directly so HIR
        Note: lowering's body-kind probe (body node offset 0 == 4002) classifies this
        Note: as an enum (type_kind 1) rather than a struct. Each variant arm becomes a
        Note: parameter node carrying the variant name (value) and, when present, its
        Note: payload type as the single child — exactly the member shape that the
        Note: field-lowering loop in lower_type_definition consumes.
        Let enum_body be proc create_ast_node from AST with 4002, stmt_line, 1
        If enum_body is equal to 0:
